section.def:
defectograph
                (鋼纜探傷儀) means any apparatus for the detection of
            broken wires in a rope;

station
                (車站) means any terminal station or intermediate
            station;

paragraph.content:
in the case of a new aerial ropeway, before the Director gives approval,
                    under section 16 of the Ordinance, to the commencement of
                    operation;
